# Ollama Fleet Configuration
# Copy to ollama-fleet.conf and customize for your network.
# This file is gitignored — do not commit your actual hosts.
#
# Format: one host per line, hostname:port
# Lines starting with # are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
# If this file is absent, the fleet client will auto-discover
# hosts on the local network and tailscale.

# Local machine (always included automatically)
# localhost:11434

# Examples — uncomment and set your hosts:
# gb10-02:11434
# agx-02:11434
# my-server.local:11434
